 The `place_pin` command can only place one pin at one time, but you provided multiple pin names. To place two pins, you should follow the script:
```
place_pin -pin_name clk -layer metal7 -location {40 30} -pin_size {1.6 2.5}
place_pin -pin_name req_val -layer metal7 -location {40 30} -pin_size {1.6 2.5}
```
